《淘气小兵兵的宽扎节》于[[北美东部时区|北美东部时区]]2001年12月11日晚20点30分通过尼克儿童频道在美国首播<ref name="Paley1" /><ref name="Source1" />，12月15和26日两度重播<ref name="Source1" />。作家斯蒂芬妮·格林（{{lang|en|Stephanie Greene}}）同年将节目剧本改编成[[繪本|繪本]]《淘气小兵兵的第一个宽扎节》（{{lang|en|''The Rugrats' First Kwanzaa''}}），[[西蒙與舒斯特|西蒙與舒斯特]]和尼克儿童频道联合出版<ref name="Book1" /><ref name="Source19">{{Cite book | title = The Rugrats' first Kwanzaa | website = [[WorldCat|WorldCat]] | oclc = 48164751}}</ref>。为了形象传达婴儿发音含混不清的效果，格林在婴儿对白中使用拼错的单词，如代表宽扎节的“{{lang|en|Kwanzaa}}”误拼成“{{lang|en|Kwonzo}}”、表示“完全正确”的“{{lang|en|exactly}}”误拼成“{{lang|en|eggsackly}}”，意为“发明家”的“{{lang|en|inventor}}”写成“{{lang|en|imbentor}}”。绘本的目标读者是四到八岁孩童，图画由塞贡多·加西亚（{{lang|en|Segundo Garcia}}）创作。<ref name="Book1">{{cite book | last = Blass | first = Rosanne J. | title = Celebrate with Books: Booktalks for Holidays and Other Occasions | year = 2005 | publisher = Libraries Unlimited | location = Santa Barbara | isbn = 978-1-59158-076-8 | ref = Blass2005 | pages = 185{{en dash}}186 | url = https://archive.org/details/celebratewithboo0000blas | accessdate = 2020-08-23}}</ref>

2001年，[[派拉蒙影業|派拉蒙影業]]发布《淘气小兵兵》特别节目{{lang|en|[[家用录像系统|VHS]]}}录像带<ref name="BookCraddock">{{cite book | last = Craddock | first = James M. | title = Video Source Book: Video program listings J–T | year = 2006 | publisher = Gale | location = Farmington Hills | page = 2443 | isbn = 978-1-4103-2499-3 | ref = Craddock2006}}</ref>，除《淘气小兵兵的宽扎节》外，里面还有两集节目和两段特殊奖励动画<ref name="Release3">{{Cite book | title = Rugrats: Kwanzaa | website = WorldCat | oclc = 48012849}}</ref>。本集由《淘气小兵兵节日收藏》（{{lang|en|''Rugrats, Holiday Collection!''}}）和《火鸡与槲寄生》（{{lang|en|''Turkey and Mistletoe''}}）的[[數碼多功能影音光碟|數碼多功能影音光碟]]收录<ref name="Release4">{{Cite web | url = https://itunes.apple.com/us/tv-season/rugrats-holiday-collection/id401010087 | title = Rugrats, Holiday Collection! | website = [[ITunes_Store|iTunes Store]] | deadurl = no | archive-date = 2019-09-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190921225417/https://itunes.apple.com/us/tv-season/rugrats-holiday-collection/id401010087}}</ref><ref name="Release1">{{Cite book | title = Turkey and mistletoe | website = WorldCat | oclc = 56403512}}</ref>。[[維亞康姆|維亞康姆]]推出节目与《淘气小兵兵》第七季其他分集的{{lang|en|DVD}}<ref name="Release2">{{Cite book | title = Rugrats. Season 7 | website = WorldCat | oclc = 879641910}}</ref>，但{{lang|en|[[ITunes_Store|iTunes Store]]}}）却将《淘气小兵兵的宽扎节》列入第八季<ref name="Release5">{{Cite web | url = https://itunes.apple.com/us/tv-season/rugrats-season-8/id867186184 | title = Rugrats, Season 8 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190621230440/https://itunes.apple.com/us/tv-season/rugrats-season-8/id867186184 | website = iTunes Store | deadurl = no | archive-date = 2019-06-21}}</ref>。本集与全剧所有分集均由《淘气小兵兵全集》收录<ref name="Release6">{{Cite web | url = https://itunes.apple.com/us/tv-season/rugrats-the-complete-series/id1436521054 | title = Rugrats, The Complete Series | website = iTunes Store | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200421103824/https://itunes.apple.com/us/tv-season/rugrats-the-complete-series/id1436521054 | archive-date = 2020-04-21}}</ref>，还可通过[[流媒体|流媒体]]和[[隨選視訊|隨選視訊]]网站观看，如[[亞馬遜影片|亞馬遜影片]]、{{lang|en|[[Hulu|Hulu]]}}和{{lang|en|[[Google_Play|Google Play]]}}<ref name="TVG1">{{Cite web | url = https://www.tvguide.com/tvshows/rugrats-2002/episode-41-season-8/quiet-please/191757/ | title = Rugrats | website = [[电视指南_(美国杂志)|TV Guide]] | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2019-04-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190417181912/https://www.tvguide.com/tvshows/rugrats-2002/episode-41-season-8/quiet-please/191757/ | archive-date = 2019-04-17}}</ref>。

2003年12月，尼克儿童频道在“尼克诞”（{{lang|en|Nickmas}}，“尼克儿童频道”开头和“圣诞”结尾的合成词）电视马拉松连播特别节目中播出《淘气小兵兵的宽扎节》<ref name="Release7">{{Cite web | url = https://www.awn.com/news/nickelodeon-deliver-nickmas-holiday-specials | title = Nickelodeon To Deliver 'Nickmas' Holiday Specials | last = Baisley | first = Sarah | date = 2003-12-16 | website = Animation World Network | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190921225319/https://www.awn.com/news/nickelodeon-deliver-nickmas-holiday-specials | archive-date = 2019-09-21}}</ref>。该频道还在“{{lang|en|NickRewind}}”（意为“尼克倒带”）的{{lang|en|[[YouTube|YouTube]]}}账户页面上传本集的两截片段<ref name="YouTube1">{{Cite web | url = https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9LQOgbJjI1Q | title = Lucy Carmichael sings 'This Little Light of Mine' | date = 2016-12-28 | website = [[YouTube|YouTube]] (NickRewind) | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190117102343/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9LQOgbJjI1Q | archive-date = 2019-01-17}}</ref><ref name="Source11" />。其中露西·卡迈克尔在教堂演唱《{{lang|en|This Little Light of Mine}}》的片段于2016年12月28日上传<ref name="YouTube1" />，马丁·路德·金出场的部分则在次年1月16日上传，以此纪念他的生日<ref name="Source11">{{Cite web | url = https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7XQvz1nq1wk | title = Martin Luther King Jr. on Rugrats | date = 2017-01-16 | website = YouTube (NickRewind) | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190116121829/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7XQvz1nq1wk | archive-date = 2019-01-16}}</ref>。2008年12月，《淘气小兵兵的宽扎节》在[[芝加哥|芝加哥]]的第14届宽扎节庆祝活动中放映<ref name="CST1">{{Cite web | url = https://www.pressreader.com/usa/chicago-sun-times/20081226/283261683710276 | title = Youth is served in Kwanzaa celebration at MXC | last = Burklow | first = Jennifer | date = 2008-12-26 | newspaper = [[芝加哥太陽報|Chicago Sun-Times]] | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190417181911/https://www.pressreader.com/usa/chicago-sun-times/20081226/283261683710276 | archive-date = 2019-04-17}}</ref>，后又在2017年12月的[[非裔公墓国家纪念碑|非裔公墓国家纪念碑]]（{{lang|en|African Burial Ground National Monument}}）活动播出<ref name="BW1">{{Cite web | url = https://www.broadwayworld.com/article/Celebrate-Kwanzaa-With-African-Burial-Ground-This-December-20171201 | title = Celebrate Kwanzaa With African Burial Ground This December | date = 2017-12-01 | website = BroadwayWorld | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190417181758/https://www.broadwayworld.com/article/Celebrate-Kwanzaa-With-African-Burial-Ground-This-December-20171201 | archive-date = 2019-04-17}}</ref>。此外，节目还与《[[淘气小兵兵的光明节|淘气小兵兵的光明节]]》一起在[[佩利媒体中心|佩利媒体中心]]（{{lang|en|Paley Center for Media}}）2019年的活动中播出<ref name="NYT1">{{Cite news | url = https://www.nytimes.com/2019/01/03/arts/events-for-children-in-nyc-this-week.html | title = 8 Things to Do With Your Kids in N.Y.C. This Weekend | last = Graeber | first = Laurel | date = 2019-01-03 | newspaper = [[纽约时报|The New York Times]] | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190417191607/https://www.nytimes.com/2019/01/03/arts/events-for-children-in-nyc-this-week.html | archive-date = 2019-04-17}}</ref>，该机构还将《淘气小兵兵的宽扎节》选入非裔美国人喜剧收藏<ref name="Paley1" />。

== 专业评价 ==
评论员称赞节目让更多观众了解宽扎节。[[极客巢穴|极客巢穴]]（{{lang|en|Den of Geek}}）和[[黑色引力|黑色引力]]网站（{{lang|en|Blavity}}，“黑色”和“地心引力”的合成词）均指出，《淘气小兵兵》已因庆祝多元化节日美名远扬<ref name="Source4">{{Cite web | url = https://blavity.com/top-5-moments-kwanzaa-television-remember | title = Do You Remember These Top 5 Moments Of Kwanzaa In Television? | last = E | first = Nita | date = 2018-12 | website = Blavity | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200603234033/https://blavity.com/top-5-moments-kwanzaa-television-remember/ | archive-date = 2020-06-03}}</ref><ref name="Source9">{{Cite web | url = https://www.denofgeek.com/tv/top-100-christmas-tv-episodes-ever-80-61/ | title = The top 100 Christmas TV episodes ever: 80–61 | last = Mead | first = Wesley | date = 2018-12-11 | website = Den of Geek | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190417181858/https://www.denofgeek.com/tv/christmas-tv/38235/top-100-christmas-tv-episodes-ever-80-61 | archive-date = 2019-04-17}}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[TheJournal.ie|TheJournal.ie]]}}网站（“{{lang|en|The Journal}}”意为“期刊”，“{{lang|en|[[.ie|.ie]]}}”是[[爱尔兰|爱尔兰]]的[[國家和地區頂級域|國家和地區頂級域]]名）发文称，《淘气小兵兵的宽扎节》很可能是部分儿童仅有的宽扎节体验<ref name="Source6">{{Cite web | url = https://www.dailyedge.ie/life-lessons-in-rugrats-3471411-Jun2017/ | title = 8 serious life lessons that The Rugrats can offer both kids and adults | date = 2017-06-30 | website = TheJournal.ie | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200526091641/https://www.dailyedge.ie/life-lessons-in-rugrats-3471411-Jun2017/ | archive-date = 2020-05-26}}</ref>。2017年，玛德琳·阿格勒（{{lang|en|Madeleine Aggeler}}）在《[[奔忙_(杂志)|奔忙]]》（''{{lang|en|Bustle}}''）杂志发文回顾《淘气小兵兵》，称赞该剧的节日特别节目认真对待小观众，没有摆出居高临下的姿态说教<ref name="Source7">{{Cite journal | url = https://www.bustle.com/p/lets-talk-about-how-rugrats-was-actually-progressive-af-66168 | title = Let's Talk About How 'Rugrats' Was Actually Progressive AF | last = Aggeler | first = Madeleine | date = 2017-07-07 | journal = Bustle | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190417182800/https://www.bustle.com/p/lets-talk-about-how-rugrats-was-actually-progressive-af-66168 | archive-date = 2019-04-17}}</ref>。《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》刊登李·马古利斯（{{lang|en|Lee Margulies}}）的文章，称《淘气小兵兵的宽扎节》能够“特别激起非裔美国观众共鸣”，因为节目的视角更加广阔，既高屋建瓴、又通过缺乏安全感的苏西视角立足现实，而不是摆出学究姿态来场[[非裔美国人历史|非裔美国人历史]]演说<ref name="Source12">{{Cite news | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-2001-dec-11-et-tips11-story.html | title = 'Rugrats' Deftly Honors Kwanzaa | last = Margulies | first = Lee | date = 2001-12-11 | newspaper = [[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]] | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190116122248/http://articles.latimes.com/2001/dec/11/entertainment/et-tips11 | archive-date = 2019-01-16}}</ref>。《[[每日先驱报|每日先驱报]]》（''{{lang|en|Daily Herald}}''）的特德·考克斯（{{lang|en|Ted Cox}}）也有类似看法，赞赏节目通过{{lang|en|T}}阿姨的行为而非空洞话语呈现非洲传统七大原则<ref name="Newspaper1">{{Cite news | url = https://www.newspapers.com/image/13866388/?terms=%22A%2BRugrats%2BKwanzaa%22 | title = Cox: ''Rugrats'' always stretches its reach | last = Cox | first = Ted | date = 2001-12-11 | access-date = 2020-08-23 | location = [[芝加哥|Chicago]] | via = Newspapers.com | newspaper = Daily Herald | archive-date = 2020-08-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200813033300/https://www.newspapers.com/image/13866388/?terms=%22A%2BRugrats%2BKwanzaa%22 | dead-url = no }}{{subscription required}}</ref>。黛博拉·福尔摩斯（{{lang|en|Deborah Holmes}}）通过《[[荷里活報道|好莱坞报道]]》赞扬本集对“黑人传统”的尊重，还称剧中向每个人传达宽扎节的信息，即任何人无论身材地位，都能贡献社会<ref name="Journal2">{{Cite journal | last = Holmes | first = Deborah | date = 2001-12-10 | title = A Rugrats Kwanzaa (Cable reviews) | url = https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=g04IAQAAMAAJ&dq=&redir_esc=y | volume = 371 | issue = 13 | pages = 28+ | access-date = 2020-08-23 | journal = [[荷里活報道|The Hollywood Reporter]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190117160322/https://books.google.com/books?id=g04IAQAAMAAJ&dq | archive-date = 2019-01-17 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。[[儿童文学|儿童文学]]学者卡特琳娜·马丁（{{lang|en|Cathlena Martin}}）赞赏《淘气小兵兵》对家庭和朋友的重视，认为这能促使人们更加“积极地了解种族和文化”<ref name="Journal1">{{Cite journal | last = Martin | first = Cathlena | date = 2008 | title = Children's Video Games as Interactive Racialization | journal = CLCWeb: Comparative Literature and Culture | volume = 10 | issue = 2 | doi = 10.7771/1481-4374.1357}}</ref>。

《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》的戴维·雷尼（{{lang|en|David Rennie}}）认为，《淘气小兵兵的宽扎节》促使宽扎节商业化，但节日创始人[[毛拉纳·卡伦加|毛拉纳·卡伦加]]（{{lang|en|Maulana Karenga}}）就对“企业界试图打入并主导宽扎节市场的举动”抱否定态度<ref name="Negative1">{{Cite news | archive-date = 2019-04-17 | url = https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/northamerica/usa/1450210/Black-Christmas-under-threat-from-the-dollar.html | title = Black Christmas under threat from the dollar | last = Rennie | first = David | date = 2003-12-26 | newspaper = [[每日电讯报|The Daily Telegraph]] | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190417184422/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/northamerica/usa/1450210/Black-Christmas-under-threat-from-the-dollar.html}}</ref>。对此[[生动媒体|生动媒体]]（{{lang|en|Livingly Media}}）的克里斯汀·洛佩兹（{{lang|en|Kristen Lopez}}）认为，《淘气小兵兵》节日特别节目已经成功“弥合讲述感人故事和充当营销工具之间的鸿沟”<ref name="Source8">{{Cite web | url = https://www.zimbio.com/Beyond+the+Tube/articles/Kl2qqo-FU2W/Holiday+TV+Specials+Simply+Marketing+Disguise | title = How Your Favorite Christmas TV Specials Do More Than Celebrate The Season | last = Lopez | first = Kristen | date = 2018-12-06 | website = Livingly Media | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190910105903/http://www.zimbio.com/Beyond+the+Tube/articles/Kl2qqo-FU2W/Holiday+TV+Specials+Simply+Marketing+Disguise | archive-date = 2019-09-10}}</ref>。

为苏西配音的[[克里·萨莫|克里·萨莫]]（{{lang|en|Cree Summer}}）获第34届[[有色人种进步协会形象奖|有色人种进步协会形象奖]][[有色人种进步协会形象奖电视类青年杰出表演奖|青年杰出表演奖]]（{{lang|en|NAACP Image Award for Outstanding Performance by a Youth}}）提名<ref name="Source15">{{Cite journal | url = https://variety.com/2001/film/awards/naacp-unveils-image-noms-1117857017/ | title = NAACP unveils Image noms | last = Stack | first = Vanessa | date = 2001-12-10 | journal = [[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]] | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190427194601/https://variety.com/2001/film/awards/naacp-unveils-image-noms-1117857017/ | archive-date = 2019-04-27}}</ref>。马古利斯称赞艾尔玛·霍尔的配音“活力四射”<ref name="Source12" />，福尔摩斯认为霍尔的演出“了不起”，萨莫也“令人愉快”<ref name="Journal2" />。

